item.title: “I’m sure he’ll play against England”: Ashton Agar assured of losing his place to Adam Zampa in T20 World Cup 2022 match against England
item.description: “I’m sure he’ll play against England”: Ashton Agar assured of losing his place to Adam Zampa in T20 World Cup 2022 match against England Ashton Agar has confirmed that Adam Zampa will be fit to play the T20 World Cup 2022 match against England on Friday.
